Help Type: topic
Topic: task

Task Routing

Create:
  spinedigest create book.sdpub ./book.md

Generate:
  spinedigest queue add book.sdpub --chapter 3 --task reading-graph --accept-cost
  spinedigest queue add book.sdpub --chapter 3 --task summary --accept-cost

Explore:
  spinedigest search book.sdpub "keyword"
  spinedigest get book.sdpub <uri>
  spinedigest related book.sdpub <uri>
  spinedigest evidence book.sdpub <uri>
  spinedigest pack book.sdpub <uri> --budget 5000
